BEGIN_PGML

It's given that [` 1 \text{ ton} = 2000 \text{ lb} `]. Do the following unit conversions.

a. [`` [$t1] \text{ tons} = ``] [__________]{$lb1} [`` \text{ lb} ``]

b. [`` [$lb2] \text{ lb} = ``] [__________]{$t2} [`` \text{ tons} ``]

END_PGML


